reviews.title: Great but buggy
reviews.comment: Eventbrite is a great but the app is poor. Crashes every time I look at event details (maybe to do with videos/pictures in the details). Very poor search functionality (string search only) AND it has no sorting. Am I really supposed to search through 1000s of events through the clunky \"load another handful of records\" each time I scroll to the bottom of the page. The development team clearly don\'t understand how their customers use this app OR the owners \"can\'t afford\" to do anything better. I\'ll re-rate once fixed and search function is enhanced.
